 \sum_{k=0}^{\lfloor {n}/{2} \rfloor}\binom{n-k+1}{k}=(c+o(1))^n 
 \max\limits_{a\leq n/2}\frac{\binom{n}{a}}{\sum_{k=0}^{a/2}\binom{n}{k}}=(c+o(1))^n 
