n
F_{n+1}=\sum_{k=0}^{\lceil n/2\rceil}\binom{n+1-k}k\;,
\sum_{k=0}^{\lfloor n/2\rfloor}\binom{n-k+1}k=\begin{cases} F_{n+1},&\text{if }n\text{ is even}\\ F_{n+1}-\binom{(n+1)/2}{(n+1)/2}=F_{n+1}-1,&\text{if }n\text{ is odd}\;. \end{cases}
